BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Markiplier Studios
DESCRIPTION:The stars are gone. The planets have disappeared. Only individ
 uals aboard space stations or starships were left to give the end a name 
 -- The Quiet Rapture. After decades of decay and crumbling infrastructure
 \, the Consolidation of Iron has made a discovery on a barren moon design
 ated AT-5. An ocean of blood. Hoping to discover desperately needed resou
 rces they immediately launch an expedition. A submarine is crafted and a 
 convict is welded inside. Due to the pressure and depth of the ocean the 
 forward viewport has been encased in metal. If successful\, they will ear
 n their freedom. If not\, another will follow. This will be the 13th expe
 dition.
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260131
DTSTAMP:20260525T030504Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260130
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Iron Lung (Theatrical Release)
